      "title": "Sita is ready to give place to Gota",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna National List Member of Parliament Mrs. Sita Arambepola said that if former President Gotabhaya Rajapaksa wants to come to the Parliament, she is ready to resign from her position.",
        "However, she also mentioned that such a request has not been made by Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna or anyone else so far"
      ],
